Clerics who take the Mysticism domain seek a better understand of their deity, and are granted spells that favor becoming closer to the divine.

<b>Domain Special Ability and Bonus Spells</b>
- Mystic Protection:  The cleric is shielded by divine will from harm once per day.  This protection grants the cleric her Cha modifier as a bonus to all saving throws for a number of rounds equal to her caster level.

- The cleric gains access to the following spells at the specified spell level: <i>Lesser Visage of the Deity (2), Righteous Might (4), Holy Word(7)</i>.